
# Minecarft: MTA



Resource for MTA, generation of landscape in Minecraft style, drawing cubes through polygons

Made as a sketch, it was not possible to implement a more optimized version at the moment, the resource will most likely remain in version v0.0.2 beta

### What is in the resource
- [x] Creating chunks
- [x] Perlin noise
- [x] Drawing chunk polygons
- [ ] Drawing optimization
- [ ] Correct drawing of polygons
- [ ] Character and camera
- [ ] Types of blocks